# 2003-09-09.wta.1: Credit Card Donations

September 9th, 2003

The following resolution has been accepted by the Board of
Directors of Software in the Public Interest, Inc.:

### WHEREAS,

1. SPI needs donations in order to conduct its business.

2. Credit card donations are a simple and effective way for people
    to donate.

3. Network for Good is providing credit card donation services to
   501(c)3 charities at a good rate.

### IT IS RESOLVED THAT,

Unless SPI's legal advisors find any problems with the terms and
services as used by Network for Good SPI will use their services for
online credit card donations.
